    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera S is an excellent driver\u2019s specimen, powered by the 3.8L M97.01 flat-six engine paired with a G97 6-speed manual transaxle. The naturally aspirated powerplant delivers a linear torque curve, while the Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) provides adjustable damping for precise lateral control. This unit features a factory short-shift kit and an upgraded Soul Performance center muffler bypass for enhanced acoustic feedback. Recent preventative maintenance includes a new Bosch alternator and a comprehensive borescope inspection to verify cylinder wall integrity. While the finish shows minor stone chips from spirited use, the chassis remains taut and the mechanical vitals are within peak operating parameters. A mechanically sound, high-engagement 911 for the dedicated purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
