      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been an absolute joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been well-taken care of and is ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
